{"tid":2152970,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"新同事自己帶茶葉返公司沖 俾我地笑到面黃","createTime":"2020-08-12T09:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T12:12:15.000Z","uid":84102,"like":26,"dislike":573,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"8ac7a2a565128e61b917a18fb74e33b2cd0c4bd4","tid":2152970,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:27:35.000Z","msg":"今日同班老細同同事開完會 大家就話不如落樓下買茶理史飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知有個00後新同事細細咁講話佢帶茶飲沖 唔駛買野飲<br />\n<br />\n我地成班呆撚咗，<br />\n<br />\n之後笑撚咗出聲，<br />\n<br />\n大聲咁問：<br />\n<br />\n「你五系窮到甘牙？」<br />\n<br />\n佢答：「唔...唔係呀，想草錢呀⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n我心諗買乜咁巴閉要草錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n之後我地打開佢櫃桶，見到成大樽普洱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地笑到仆街，大大聲佢 啲茶葉係咪你自己種？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我地拎個樽出黎打開，<br />\n<br />\n將佢啲垃圾茶葉掉曬落垃圾桶，<br />\n<br />\n佢即刻衝上黎想打鳩我地咁款不過比人㩒住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n<br />\n掉曬之後就咁掉番個吉樽放入櫃桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢仲眼濕濕想喊咁，<br />\n<br />\n笑到我地仆街，<br />\n<br />\n之後我地成班人每人出少少請佢飲杯蘋果烏龍少甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪窮到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"610b2d0ad7173eb67b8ba37f4c02aedf804ec33d","tid":2152970,"uid":105619,"like":30,"dislike":3,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:38:02.000Z","msg":"好得閒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d841ce37e6601fe79742387961b5dde243314779","tid":2152970,"uid":195248,"like":86,"dislike":1,"score":85,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:40:32.000Z","msg":"東京中央增設「一期一會」普洱專拍以來，一直叫好叫座。去年香港秋拍，百年「藍票宋聘號」連佣HK$1,332萬成交，打破紀錄成為史上最貴「普洱茶王」。今季再下一城，百年「福元昌號」以HK$2,632萬成交，刷新紀錄榮登「茶王」寶座。"},{"pid":"f49a3ffe9cc203c009ba6f3c43c01c09bdd5a395","tid":2152970,"uid":304047,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:42:45.000Z","msg":"知慳識儉有咩問題呢？<br />\n反而係你地bully人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1041067f7431874cf65e7fc9d1a78101ce88612","tid":2152970,"uid":31200,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:45:40.000Z","msg":"On9當有趣"},{"pid":"dc62be93ef951e4813977950d4ea864fdb38254c","tid":2152970,"uid":7482,"like":60,"dislike":3,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />假膠都有咁多人認真"},{"pid":"a1a26f67cb1b4d28ed727d04e7f2c2749c2060bf","tid":2152970,"uid":306109,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"8ac7a2a565128e61b917a18fb74e33b2cd0c4bd4","tid":2152970,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:27:35.000Z","msg":"今日同班老細同同事開完會 大家就話不如落樓下買茶理史飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知有個00後新同事細細咁講話佢帶茶飲沖 唔駛買野飲<br />\n<br />\n我地成班呆撚咗，<br />\n<br />\n之後笑撚咗出聲，<br />\n<br />\n大聲咁問：<br />\n<br />\n「你五系窮到甘牙？」<br />\n<br />\n佢答：「唔...唔係呀，想草錢呀⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n我心諗買乜咁巴閉要草錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n之後我地打開佢櫃桶，見到成大樽普洱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地笑到仆街，大大聲佢 啲茶葉係咪你自己種？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我地拎個樽出黎打開，<br />\n<br />\n將佢啲垃圾茶葉掉曬落垃圾桶，<br />\n<br />\n佢即刻衝上黎想打鳩我地咁款不過比人㩒住<img src=\"